<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="<%=require('assets/misc/favicon.png')%>" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Spartan:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Frontend Mentor | Social Proof Section</title>
  </head>
  <body class="">
    <main>
      <header>
        <h1 class="title">10,000+ of our users love our products.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          We only provide great products combined with excellent customer service. See what our satisfied customers are saying about our
          services.
        </p>
      </header>

      <ul class="reviews">
        <li class="review xl:self-start"><p>Rated 5 Stars in Reviews</p></li>
        <li class="review"><p>Rated 5 Stars in Report Guru</p></li>
        <li class="review xl:self-end"><p>Rated 5 Stars in BestTech</p></li>
      </ul>

      <ul class="quotes">
        <li class="quote">
          <div class="quote__header">
            <img src="<%=require('assets/buyer/image-colton.jpg')%> alt="colton" class="quote__image" />
            <h2 class="quote__name">Colton Smith</h2>
            <h3 class="quote__status">Verified Buyer</h3>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="quote_text">
            We needed the same printed design as the one we had ordered a week prior. Not only did they find the original order, but we also
            received it in time. Excellent!
          </blockquote>
        </li>
        <li class="quote xl:mt-8">
          <div class="quote__header">
            <img src="<%=require('assets/buyer/image-irene.jpg')%>" alt="irene" class="quote__image" />
            <h2 class="quote__name">Irene Roberts</h2>
            <h3 class="quote__status">Verified Buyer</h3>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="quote_text">
            Customer service is always excellent and very quick turn around. Completely delighted with the simplicity of the purchase and
            the speed of delivery.
          </blockquote>
        </li>
        <li class="quote xl:mt-16">
          <div class="quote__header">
            <img src="<%=require('assets/buyer/image-anne.jpg')%>" alt="anne" class="quote__image" />
            <h2 class="quote__name">Anne Wallace</h2>
            <h3 class="quote__status">Verified Buyer</h3>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="quote_text">
            Put an order with this company and can only praise them for the very high standard. Will definitely use them again and recommend
            them to everyone!
          </blockquote>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
